{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"3fc49c8245","title":"彭德怀遗言","origin":"彭德怀传记编写组《一个真正的人——彭德怀》，人民出版社1994年10月第一版。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"1e5a187618","index":0,"year":1974,"month":9,"day":2,"articleId":"3fc49c8245"}],"tags":[{"id":"994fc035d4","name":"工业战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"ae0a6697a5","name":"彭德怀","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"dd94b19278","name":"彭德怀"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"d2bc07959c","type":"title","text":"彭德怀遗言","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3fc49c8245"},{"id":"ff73e88653","type":"authors","text":"彭德怀","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3fc49c8245"},{"id":"820c25f49d","type":"subtitle","text":"〖1974年9月2日上午，两个专案审查人员奉叶剑英之命到医院看望彭德怀，作临终谈话。这是他们记录的谈话要点。〗","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3fc49c8245"},{"id":"f8a47b49df","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席发展了马列主义……","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3fc49c8245"},{"id":"c8406b029b","type":"paragraph","text":"周总理，我们相处三十多年，他是我们党内最能掌握和运用毛主席思想策略的，我们的社会主义事业一定能胜利。","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3fc49c8245"},{"id":"a147e25365","type":"paragraph","text":"我自己犯有很多错误，但我不搞阴谋诡计，在这点上我是清白的。","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3fc49c8245"},{"id":"c343948f26","type":"paragraph","text":"问心无愧！","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3fc49c8245"},{"id":"4d64d5bab0","type":"paragraph","text":"我们国防建设，战略防御设施不完备，国防工业和科研跟不上，这是我最担心的，只要我们有计划，有准备，敌人的物质力量是可以战胜的。","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3fc49c8245"},{"id":"1591adb9af","type":"paragraph","text":"已经审查我八年了，现在还没有做结论。","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3fc49c8245"}],"page":{"id":"14f0b37221","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3fc49c8245","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}